OL,3,CAll residents staying at the Bell
OL,4,CHotel 'have been removed', council says
OL,6,FAll residents at The Bell Hotel in
OL,7,FEssex, which has been used to house
OL,8,Fasylum seekers and was the location of
OL,9,Fprotests last year, have been removed
OL,10,Ffrom the property, Epping Forest
OL,11,FDistrict Council said.
OL,13,FOn Thursday, the council said it was
OL,14,Faware the Home Office had vacated all
OL,15,Fthose staying at the hotel and that
OL,16,Fonly security staff remained onsite.
OL,18,FLast year, the location became the
OL,19,Ffocus of protests after hotel resident
OL,20,FHadush Kebatu sexually assaulted a 14-
OL,21,Fyear-old girl.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
