OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781453487
OL,3,CAll residents staying at the Bell
OL,4,CHotel 'have been removed', council says
OL,6,FKebatu was found guilty of five
OL,7,Foffences ` including sexual assault `
OL,8,Fand jailed, and was then mistakenly
OL,9,Freleased from HMP Chelmsford last
OL,10,FOctober before he was detained and
OL,11,Fdeported to Ethiopia.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Epping Forest District
OL,14,FCouncil said: "Despite ongoing
OL,15,Fengagement with the Home Office, we
OL,16,Fdid not know in advance that this was
OL,17,Fgoing to happen.
