OL,3,CAll residents staying at the Bell
OL,4,CHotel 'have been removed', council says
OL,6,F"We are seeking clarification from the
OL,7,FHome Office on the details of what has
OL,8,Fhappened and what their next steps
OL,9,Fwill be."
OL,11,FThe Home Office said: "The government
OL,12,Fis removing the incentives drawing
OL,13,Fillegal migrants to Britain. We are
OL,14,Fclosing every asylum hotel and moving
OL,15,Fasylum seekers into basic
OL,16,Faccommodation including ex-military
OL,17,Fsites.
