OL,3,CAll residents staying at the Bell
OL,4,CHotel 'have been removed', council says
OL,6,F"The population of asylum seekers in
OL,7,Fhotels has fallen by 35% in the last
OL,8,Fyear and by 63% from the peak under
OL,9,Fthe previous government."
